{"tid":1536974,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再講沒有暴徒","createTime":"2019-09-03T18:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:28:40.000Z","uid":111088,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"72897da7a182c765b9a05918be711eb74e093765","tid":1536974,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:31:53.000Z","msg":"想講好耐<br />\n一開始句野係「沒有暴徒 只有暴政」<br />\n回應緊「撤回暴動定性」呢個訴求<br />\n唔知幾時開始錯吓錯吓變左沒有暴徒<br />\n屌你老母邊撚度冇暴徒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲催淚彈橡膠子彈好似唔撚洗錢咁掉<br />\n四五個人圍住一個冇反抗力嘅大棍大棍毆落去<br />\n布包袋例牌瞄要害<br />\n一個新屋嶺打到三十幾個人骨折<br />\n你話我知呢啲唔撚叫暴徒叫乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同我記撚返住</span></span></strong><br />\n唔撚係冇暴徒，暴徒個統稱叫<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察(+滲入嘅解放軍)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4a426ba37be1455dda13f46ae7c725607624c25c","tid":1536974,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:32:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br 